#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:238 c321f8010e554f9bb3054a4a9051144d
msgid ""
"Check the status of the TMOSUnit and execute the corresponding callback "
"functions based on the event flags."
msgstr "检查 TMOSUnit 的状态，并根据事件标志执行相应的回调函数。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:240 add55632351147849ecac86e13aae0b1
msgid ""
"This method should be called periodically to poll the sensor status and "
"handle any detected events."
msgstr "该方法应定期调用，用于轮询传感器状态并处理检测到的任何事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:242 fdc8e02ac01f4164a630a38ccb16fe37
msgid ""
"It checks the following flags and triggers the associated callbacks if "
"the flags are set:"
msgstr "它会检查以下标志位，并在标志位被设置时触发对应的回调函数："

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:244 bd6f2a68d30446438b267bf3ceba38b5
msgid "``ambient temperature`` (0): Indicates an ambient temperature shock event."
msgstr "``ambient temperature`` (0)：表示环境温度冲击事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:245 4e5f635b70ee4ff9abfefc91045a635a
msgid "``motion`` (1): Indicates a motion detection event."
msgstr "``motion`` (1)：表示检测到运动事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:246 c3ebd7643b3148719d78a0fd2394a348
msgid "``presence`` (2): Indicates a presence detection event."
msgstr "``presence`` (2)：表示一次存在检测事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:247 0dc4b1bb63a244b58dab1c7dcf6ee36d
msgid ""
"``ambient temperature not`` (3): Indicates an ambient temperature shock "
"event has not occurred."
msgstr "``ambient temperature not`` (3)：表示未发生环境温度冲击事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:248 31c601dbdd5245299f73019eef0c3fd2
msgid "``motion not`` (4): Indicates a motion detection event has not occurred."
msgstr "``motion not`` (4)：表示未发生运动检测事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:249 418169e49e4248b9af2f591e01f87852
msgid ""
"``presence not`` (5): Indicates a presence detection event has not "
"occurred."
msgstr "``presence not`` (5)：表示未发生存在检测事件。"

#: ../../source/unit/tmos.rst:251 b88dd3abe4c24e2499984c827febeb1f
msgid ""
"The callback functions associated with these events are set using the "
":meth:`set_callback` method."
msgstr "与这些事件关联的回调函数通过 :meth:`set_callback` 方法进行设置。"

